1@S – 2@C (or 2@D or 2@H) 
3@S

When you ^*Bjump^*N rebid your suit in this auction, you are advertising both a 6 card suit and also one that can be trumps opposite a small singleton 
So the minimum quality suit is KQJ9xx
That suit is (usually) going to play for 1 loser opposite a singleton
In 2 over 1, jumps below game promise solid suits.

